Compass RE Texas, LLC - The Woodlands

data.description: Beautiful 1.5 story home situated on a wooded lot with quick access to Beltway 8 and no neighbors behind features high ceilings, recessed lighting & hardwood-like ceramic tile floors throughout the living areas. Open floor plan with two-story foyer & wrought iron staircase leads to living room with windows overlooking the side yard & flows seamlessly to dining room w/chandelier lighting & window seat. Island kitchen with breakfast bar & pendant lighting touts Shaker-style cabinets highlighted by quartz counters & decorative tile back splash w/lighting, S/S appliances including a 4-burner gas range & refrigerator stays. Owner’s suite has private bath with vanity, soaking tub, glass enclosed shower & closet w/built-in dressers. Secondary bedrooms have convenient access to full bath & utility room with washer/dryer. Upstairs game room w/new carpet & full bath could be 4th bedroom. Backyard is perfect for entertaining with 18x7 covered patio with a natural gas stub for barbecue grill.
